NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|As to the play. the reason roberta should play 2nd hand low is that she should assume that if duffer had the Ace of spades, she would take the finesse. You need to think about this type of issue when deciding how to defend. If duffer being tricky and leading low from Ace, then publicly say "congratulations" and privately think North made a mistake and got away with it.|
