cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|There was no game try on this hand. But if you play for example, 1S-2S-3C denies club cards, that is alertable. If you play it shows club cards, but may be a short suit, that is not alertable. Most people play that auction shows club cards, and is asking partner to value club cards as well when deciding whether or not to bid game.|
